Dungeons & Dragons - Cutter 01 (of 05) (2013)

image


English | CBR | 22 pages | 37.29 MB|Published April 2013

Cover by Steve Ellis (W) Geno Salvatore, R. A. Salvatore (A) David Baldeon BIRTHRIGHT! Tierflin and Doum'weille are half-Drow siblings, locked in competition for the ownership of the bloodthirsty sword Khazid'hea-the Cutter! Their father, the Drow renegade Tos'un-a veteran of battles against the Kingdom of Many-Arrows-is forced to choose his heir... but what does the powerful sword have to say on the subject?

image


English | CBR | 24 pages | 40.70 MB|Published May 2013

Cover by Steve Ellis (W) Geno Salvatore, R. A. Salvatore (A) David Baldeon Tragedy strikes a peaceful Moon Elf village-and at the heart is Tos'un and Sinnafain's children: their half-drow daughter Doum'wielle and her brother Tos'un. And driving the tragedy is the bloodthirsty sentient sword Khazid'hea-a blade known for driving its wielders into savage madness!

English | CBR | 25 pages | 41.45 MB|Published June 2013

Cover by Steve Ellis (W) Geno Salvatore, R. A. Salvatore (A) David Baldeon ON THE RUN! But will that protect her from the rage of the Moon Elves?

Dungeons & Dragons - Cutter 05 (of 05) (2013)

image


English | CBR | 25 pages | 34 MB |Published September 2013

Cover by Steve Ellis (W) Geno Salvatore, R. A. Salvatore (A) David Baldeon THE JOURNEY ENDS! Doum'wielle Armago-wielder of the malevolent sentient sword Khazid'hea, the Cutter-confronts her pursuers. But will they be able to pull her back from the brink of savage madness? The conclusion will shock you!
